commit.message:
Use multi-stage docker builds

By doing this I was able to remove the compiled JS code

Minor fixes

Fixed a few little issues around

Cleanup and compiled clojure

The clojure wouldn't compile in the Docker container so I
am just committing it.

Also cleaned some other stuff up.

ToDo list in ClojureScript

Because I am insane I wanted to add another useless feature.

Because I am *very* insane I decided to do it in ClojureScript.

So yeah, here is a simple ToDo manager with LocalStorage saving
written in ClojureScript.
